      <h1 class="reveal visible text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-['DM_Serif_Display',serif] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-[#1d1d1f]">
        Façonner<span class="italic">,</span><br />
        <span class="italic">le web</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal visible reveal-delay-1 mt-6 text-base sm:text-lg text-black/40 leading-relaxed">
        WordPress, sites sur mesure, applications. 
        Chaque projet est pensé, conçu et livré avec une obsession : la qualité.
      </p>
      <div class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2 mt-8 flex items-center gap-5">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#1d1d1f] text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-200">
          Démarrer un projet
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="text-sm text-black/40 hover:text-black/70 transition-colors">En savoir plus</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative bg-[#f5f5f7] overflow-hidden sm:col-span-1">
    <img
      src="/me.png"
